				</SampleCodeColumn>
				<SampleCodeResultContainer>
					<PositionExampleResult />
					<br>
					<p class="small">Por defecto los elementos tienen position: static;</p>
					<br>
					<p class="small">Se posicionan de acuerdo al flujo normal del documento y no se puede reposicionar.</p>
				</SampleCodeResultContainer>
			</SampleCodeColumns>
		</Slide>
		<Slide title="Posición relativa">
			<SampleCodeColumns>
				<SampleCodeColumn>
					<SampleCode language="CSS">
						<pre style="font-family:monospace;color: rgb(201, 209, 217); background-color: rgb(13, 17, 23); font-weight: 400; "><span style="color: rgb(121, 192, 255); font-weight: 400;">.contenedor</span> <SampleCodeBrackets>
						<SampleCodeTab /><span style="color: rgb(121, 192, 255); font-weight: 400;">position</span>: static; <span style="color: rgb(139, 148, 158); font-weight: 400;">/<span></span>* valor por defecto */</span>
						</SampleCodeBrackets>
						<span style="color: rgb(121, 192, 255); font-weight: 400;">.bulbasaur</span> <SampleCodeBrackets>
						<SampleCodeTab /><span style="color: rgb(121, 192, 255); font-weight: 400;">position</span>: relative;
						<SampleCodeTab /><span style="color: rgb(121, 192, 255); font-weight: 400;">bottom</span>: <span style="color: rgb(121, 192, 255); font-weight: 400;">60px</span>;
						<SampleCodeTab /><span style="color: rgb(121, 192, 255); font-weight: 400;">left</span>: <span style="color: rgb(121, 192, 255); font-weight: 400;">60px</span>;
						</SampleCodeBrackets></pre>
					</SampleCode>
				</SampleCodeColumn>
				<SampleCodeResultContainer>
					<PositionExampleResult stage="relative" />
					<br>
					<p class="small">Cuando la posición es relativa, el elemento se posicionan de acuerdo al flujo normal del documento, pero se puede reposicionar.</p>
					<br>
					<p class="small">Las propiedades top, bottom, left o right permiten desplazarlo respecto de su ubicación original.</p>
				</SampleCodeResultContainer>
			</SampleCodeColumns>
		</Slide>
		<Slide title="Posición absoluta">
			<SampleCodeColumns>
				<SampleCodeColumn>
					<SampleCode language="CSS">
						<pre style="font-family:monospace;color: rgb(201, 209, 217); background-color: rgb(13, 17, 23); font-weight: 400; "><span style="color: rgb(121, 192, 255); font-weight: 400;">.contenedor</span> <SampleCodeBrackets>
						<SampleCodeTab /><span style="color: rgb(121, 192, 255); font-weight: 400;">position</span>: relative; <span style="color: rgb(139, 148, 158); font-weight: 400;"></span>
						</SampleCodeBrackets>
						<span style="color: rgb(121, 192, 255); font-weight: 400;">.bulbasaur</span> <SampleCodeBrackets>
						<SampleCodeTab /><span style="color: rgb(121, 192, 255); font-weight: 400;">position</span>: relative;
						<SampleCodeTab /><span style="color: rgb(121, 192, 255); font-weight: 400;">bottom</span>: <span style="color: rgb(121, 192, 255); font-weight: 400;">60px</span>;
						<SampleCodeTab /><span style="color: rgb(121, 192, 255); font-weight: 400;">left</span>: <span style="color: rgb(121, 192, 255); font-weight: 400;">60px</span>;
						</SampleCodeBrackets>
						<span style="color: rgb(121, 192, 255); font-weight: 400;">.squirtle</span> <SampleCodeBrackets>
						<SampleCodeTab /><span style="color: rgb(121, 192, 255); font-weight: 400;">position</span>: absolute;
						<SampleCodeTab /><span style="color: rgb(121, 192, 255); font-weight: 400;">top</span>: <span style="color: rgb(121, 192, 255); font-weight: 400;">120px</span>;
						<SampleCodeTab /><span style="color: rgb(121, 192, 255); font-weight: 400;">left</span>: <span style="color: rgb(121, 192, 255); font-weight: 400;">10px</span>;
						</SampleCodeBrackets></pre>
					</SampleCode>
				</SampleCodeColumn>
				<SampleCodeResultContainer>
					<PositionExampleResult stage="absolute" />
					<br>
					<p class="small">Cuando la posición es absoluta, el elemento es removido del flujo del documento, no se le reserva su espacio.</p>
					<br>
					<p class="small">Las propiedades top, bottom, left o right permiten posicionarlo respecto a su ancestro posicionado más cercano.</p>
				</SampleCodeResultContainer>
			</SampleCodeColumns>
		</Slide>
		<Slide title="Posición absoluta">
			<SampleCodeColumns>
				<SampleCodeColumn>
					<SampleCode language="CSS">
						<pre style="font-family:monospace;color: rgb(201, 209, 217); background-color: rgb(13, 17, 23); font-weight: 400; "><span style="color: rgb(121, 192, 255); font-weight: 400;">.contenedor</span> <SampleCodeBrackets>
							<SampleCodeTab /><span style="color: rgb(121, 192, 255); font-weight: 400;">position</span>: static; <span style="color: rgb(139, 148, 158); font-weight: 400;">/<span></span>* valor por defecto */</span>
						</SampleCodeBrackets>
						<span style="color: rgb(121, 192, 255); font-weight: 400;">.bulbasaur</span> <SampleCodeBrackets>
						<SampleCodeTab /><span style="color: rgb(121, 192, 255); font-weight: 400;">position</span>: relative;
						<SampleCodeTab /><span style="color: rgb(121, 192, 255); font-weight: 400;">bottom</span>: <span style="color: rgb(121, 192, 255); font-weight: 400;">60px</span>;
						<SampleCodeTab /><span style="color: rgb(121, 192, 255); font-weight: 400;">left</span>: <span style="color: rgb(121, 192, 255); font-weight: 400;">60px</span>;
